{"tid":1666372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼二百流浮山刀手後元朗鄉黑五千大軍出動","createTime":"2019-10-21T03:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:22:46.000Z","uid":171139,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1746703aac31656f8959af286e2d38712f0b7724","tid":1666372,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有份參「保衞戰」的村民表示，單是南邊圍、西邊圍、燒烤樂園一帶已佈下天羅地網，「佢哋一衝入南邊圍已有5,000人招呼，我哋再喺後面包抄，（示威者）冇得走。」最終因警方加派人手，加上示威者未有入村，才煞停「元朗恐襲2.0」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼二百流浮山刀手後又一力作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n727個日咪推左入西邊圍村口囉，五千大軍去左邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班西邊圍村民仲喺度講加油，支持我哋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水喉鐵呢<br />\n<br />\n講到咁口響，今晚夠薑咪再嚟料囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我等緊你五千大軍包抄我哋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66dd5afe8a77ae301d6c9e37ceadcfffcbccd1a","tid":1666372,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ddb8165550bba103a259399c29aebad54e5481","tid":1666372,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"1021"},{"pid":"df3797c2f406c48d7e405c6248aff3c2fd085c04","tid":1666372,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:21:4